➜香港特区教育局：全港学校将如期开学 只能网上授课
http://www.sohu.com/a/411254917_162522	36881
<p><span>来源：<span>海外网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-08-03 18:02</p>
<p><i><img src="//p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200803/87327b42c56045b38891b8269e6c083a.png" /></i></p>
